# TC_02 - Accessibility: font size scaling [iOS]

## Preconditions:
- Enable the feature flag for Large Fonts support on the Transaction History screen

## Test Steps:
1. Open iOS Settings
2. Go to Display & Brightness → Text Size
3. Increase font size to maximum
4. Open banking app
5. Navigate through Transaction History screen

## Expected Result:
- Text is readable and not cut off
- No UI overlap or broken layout
- Buttons remain clickable
- No horizontal scrolling appears
- All key actions remain accessible

## Notes:
- App should support dynamic font scaling (accessibility compliance)

# TC_02 - Accessibility: font size scaling [Android]

## Preconditions:
- Enable the feature flag for Large Fonts support on the Transaction History screen

## Test Steps (Android):
1. Open Settings
2. Go to Display → Font size
3. Set font to largest option
4. Open banking app
5. Navigate through Transaction History screen

## Expected Result:
- Text is readable and not cut off
- No UI overlap or broken layout
- Buttons remain clickable
- No horizontal scrolling appears
- All key actions remain accessible